  "texts": [
    "One could also worry about what targeted predictions enable, namely, micro-targeting.",
    "One controversial aspect of the collaboration between cutting-edge technology and political actors came to light in March 2018, as the world learned about Cambridge Analytica (CA).",
    "The marketing-hyped selling point of the company was as follows: by collecting and analysing Big Data from Facebook profiles, they were able to accurately predict where any individual would lie on the Big-five personality traits scales.",
    "Further, they asserted to have discovered a remarkable statistical regularity: political messaging which was attuned to individuals personality was more likely to succeed in changing their mind.",
    "AI polling is what makes micro-targeting highly effective."
  ],
